    "1. **Logistic Regression:** A classic model that looks at word importance using TF-IDF.\n",
    "2. **LSTM:** A deep learning model that is good at understanding the order of words in a sentence.\n",
    "\n",
    "I'll train them on social media and then test them on our student dataset!"
